Since you are creating new SLPs in all the tests separately with your choice of evidences with diff status, defining things in @Before will be good. Lets follow DRY. The first 3 lines can be taken out into @Before. That will help you achieve this.

		final TaEnum&lt;EvidenceResultType&gt; evidenceResultWaived = new TaEnum&lt;EvidenceResultType&gt;(EvidenceResultType.WAIVED);
		final TaEnum&lt;EvidenceResultType&gt; evidenceResultNotSatisfied = new TaEnum&lt;EvidenceResultType&gt;(EvidenceResultType.NOT_SATISFIED);
		final TaEnum&lt;EvidenceResultType&gt; evidenceResultPending = new TaEnum&lt;EvidenceResultType&gt;(EvidenceResultType.PENDING);
		final SelectedLeavePlan selectedLeavePlan = SelectedLeavePlanBuilder.builder().withLeaveRequest(leaveRequest).build();
		EvidenceResultBuilder.builder().withEvidenceResultType(evidenceResultWaived).withSelectedLeavePlan(selectedLeavePlan).build();
		EvidenceResultBuilder.builder().withEvidenceResultType(evidenceResultNotSatisfied).withSelectedLeavePlan(selectedLeavePlan).build();
		EvidenceResultBuilder.builder().withEvidenceResultType(evidenceResultPending).withSelectedLeavePlan(selectedLeavePlan).build();

Same applies to the first part of the other review comments too.

